reviewText: Have been looking for episodes not included in 1st half of season
Very very touching two episodes of the Ponderosa series. Just wish we could get the whole series and not just half.
I really like the Bonanza show and wanted to have these later shows.
Good films. Took a bit of getting used to with not having the 4 original Bonanza actors.
Good family entertainment. Fun to think of what happened before Bonanza. Would recomment it to families. Good clean tv show
